  "title": "Dental Assistant #82053",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Dental Clinic</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Dental Assistant</strong></li><li>Working Location: Orchard</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5-days (Mon-Fri: 9am-5pm, Sat: 9am-1pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic salary $2,200 - $2,800 + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Assist dentists during consultations and dental procedures.</li><li>Ensure patient comfort throughout treatments.</li><li>Provide basic oral health instructions.</li><li>Prepare necessary materials, dental instruments, and equipment.</li><li>Sterilize instruments and prepare the dental room.</li><li>Maintain cleanliness in treatment rooms through general housekeeping.</li><li>Set up appointments and follow up on patient inquiries.</li><li>Perform other duties as assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum PSLE or equivalent.</li><li>Good Communication and Interpersonal skills.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#82053 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
